crime_comedy.title: Crime Comedy
crime_comedy.description: Crime doesn’t pay, but it can make you laugh!

9352.title: Half a Sinner
9352.description: A young and beautiful school teacher Anne Gladden fears a dull future. She finally decides to take a walk on the wild side in order to find adventure, which is just what she finds.

229883.title: My Favorite Brunette
229883.description: A wannabe gumshoe finds himself framed for murder while working for a beautiful brunette in this uproarious send-up of hard-boiled detective films.

293267.title: Key of Life
293267.description: A case of stolen identity and one determined bride-to-be intersect in this comedic escapade from famed Japanese filmmaker Kenji Uchida. Official Selection - Toronto Int'l Film Festival

299580.title: The Big Easy
299580.description: A new female district attorney is unhappy with the gangs and corruption in New Orleans and bonds with a detective in this sultry crime thriller.

299591.title: Suicide Kings
299591.description: A group of rich twenty-somethings kidnap a crime boss and use his money to pay a ransom for one of their sisters, who was also kidnapped.

300175.title: Stand Up Guys
300175.description: After one of them gets paroled, three retired gangsters reunite and reminisce as another ponders his next job — killing his old friend.

300836.title: Homer & Eddie
300836.description: A mentally challenged man gets help from a sociopathic woman when he tries to reunite with his dying father, who disowned him years earlier.

303090.title: The January Man
303090.description: A killer comedy that has an ex-cop trailing a serial murderer... and the mayor's sexy daughter!  Kevin Kline leads an all-star cast that includes Susan Sarandon, Mary Elizabeth Mastrantonio, Harvey Keitel and Rod Steiger.

307755.title: Novocaine
307755.description: The hilarious Steve Martin stars in this darkly comic tale of a good man gone bad featuring Helena Bonham Carter, Laura Dern, and Scott Caan.

310130.title: Fatal Instinct
310130.description: Comic director Carl Reiner packs this off-the-wall spoof with gags that pay homage to erotic thriller classics.

317189.title: Fatal Beauty
317189.description: When a tainted drug shipment hits the streets of L.A., a witty narcotics cop goes undercover to investigate in this fast-paced romantic comedy.

324856.title: Bank Roll
324856.description: Six friends have three days to pull off one heist.

343050.title: Big Money Hustlas
343050.description: When the NYPD can't stop a ruthless crime lord, they recruit an eccentric and charismatic cop from San Francisco to get the job done once and for all.

356526.title: Be Cool
356526.description: Chili Palmer turns to the world of rock stars, pop divas, and hip hop gangstas when a new idea for a movie leads him into the music business.

376106.title: I Went Down
376106.description: Irish action comedy written by Conor McPherson and directed by Paddy Breathnach, starring Brendan Gleeson and Peter McDonald. Git is an ex-con freshly released from a stint in prison. He soon finds himself thrust into the shady criminal underworld by crime boss Tom French, who forces him into taking on a task for him. He is teamed up with Bunny - a quick tempered brute who offed his own grandfather, and set the challenge of taking a hostage. Although their relationship gets off to a frosty start, the pair soon realise that if they are to survive the brutal underworld they must work together.

385363.title: Barney Thomson
385363.description: An awkward, diffident, Glasgow barber, lives a life of desperate mediocrity until he enters the grotesque and comically absurd world of the serial killer.

386449.title: Vice Academy 2
386449.description: Two rookie cops pose as strippers to get the drop on a villainess plotting to spike L.A.'s water with aphrodisiacs.

399204.title: After School Special
399204.description: Two high school kids mentored by a nightclub owner go on a mission to find their classmate after she is kidnapped by a secret society.

400849.title: Sunshine Cleaning
400849.description: A once-popular single mother-turned-maid gets a new lease on life when she gets into the lucrative world of crime scene cleanup with her sister’s help.

402015.title: Too Fat Too Furious
402015.description: A clumsy, overweight criminal carrying a hefty debt teams up with a motley crew of undesirables to steal $300,000 to buy his father's new liver.

405682.title: Mystery Date
405682.description: In order to win the woman of his dreams, a young man pretends to be his older brother.

413164.title: Freeway
413164.description: A teenage delinquent goes to live with her grandmother but on her way, she meets a charming serial killer and things go downhill from there.

414101.title: Jonny's Sweet Revenge
414101.description: A hilarious dark comedy about a couple returning to their roots as petty criminals in a last-ditch effort to save their struggling relationship. As the plan quickly falls apart, an offbeat ensemble take part in an absurd LA hostage crisis.

416212.title: Chasing
416212.description: A wealthy CEO Seung-joo and Jeong-taek, a homicide detective, have had a strange nemesis-like relationship for over twenty years. One night, Seung-joo gets robbed by four delinquent high schoolers who even took Jeong-taek’s gun. Now Seung-joo and Jeong-taek must work together to find the brazen boys. Can these two men set aside their differences and retrieve their belongings from the boys?

417608.title: Hoods
417608.description: A middle-aged mobster teams up with five would-be gangsters to take out the son of a rival mob boss, only to discover their target is a nine-year-old boy.

417614.title: Holy Hustle
417614.description: On the run from gangsters, a quick-witted conman and his straight-laced brother scheme their way into pastoring a downtrodden church as a hideout.

417710.title: Buttwhistle
417710.description: Ogden Confer is a community college student living with his parents and coping with the recent loss of his best friend, Rose. When he prevents the suicide effort of a mysterious young lady, Beth, she makes him pay for not minding his own business.

439637.title: Smartass
439637.description: A 15-year old runaway is released from jail after being arrested and hustled. Now she must navigate Murder City, 120 miles away from anyone familiar.

440279.title: London's Finest
440279.description: A dirty cop pursues a vendetta against some small time London drug-dealers hiding a shipment of heroin, along with the help of gun-toting roughnecks.

443633.title: Silver Bears
443633.description: When a shady but alluring duo, a prince and a wheeler-dealer, try to take over a Swiss bank, they end up with a silver mine and romantic problems.

445664.title: Red Ribbon Blues
445664.description: In this unique tale of modern day vigilantism, a group of activists declare war against the drug company establishment. This HIV support group turned warriors are determined to receive the attention and treatment they feel they are being denied, and plan a heist to steal the medication that they need.

449195.title: Scramble
449195.description: When his girlfriend is kidnapped by a sex trafficking ring, a young man will do anything, including confronting gangster and killers, to get her back.

449512.title: Fifty Pills
449512.description: A college guy doesn’t just have to go through a series of escapades to date his dream girl, he has to sell 50 ecstasy pills to pay his tuition bill.

452576.title: Flickering Lights
452576.description: They have always had each other, now they just have to find themselves.

458488.title: Rim Shop
458488.description: Jo Jo has 24 hours to pay off a vicious loan shark, or lose his rim shop forever. His only hope is in the hands of his two idiotic friends.

460624.title: Don't Get Caught
460624.description: After stealing weed from a marijuana farm, a young man races to repay the gang of hillbilly bikers who are now holding his girlfriend hostage.

460878.title: The Art of the Steal
460878.description: Loyalty and the bonds of brotherhood are tested when a high-stakes heist is planned by a crew of criminals, each with an ulterior motive.

461500.title: How to Be a Serial Killer
461500.description: A man teaches the perfect method of getting your life on track and having a meaningful existence in this parody of self-help and motivational gurus.

461819.title: The Job
461819.description: Unemployed and eager to marry his girlfriend, a man takes a job from a drifter but realizes he may be out of his depth when it turns out to be a hit.

462426.title: Assassination of a High School President
462426.description: At a Catholic high school, the popular girl teams up with a sophomore newspaper reporter to investigate a case of stolen SAT exams. Once the duo target their suspects, a larger conspiracy is unearthed.

463728.title: Big Bad Mama
463728.description: A pistol-packing mother and her gorgeous daughters embark on a string of daring bank heists across Depression-era America in this cult classic.

463794.title: The Cartier Affair
463794.description: Convict Curt Taylor owes a substantial sum to Phil Drexler, the top dog at California State Prison. When Curt is released from prison, he becomes a secretary for Cartier Rand in order to steal her jewels and settle the debt with Drexler. During the course of his tenure as secretary, Curt unexpectedly falls in love with his employer, muddling his motivation to steal from her. Cartier soon showcases similar sentiments, and the two engage in a love affair.

464490.title: Robbery
464490.description: Ping's night shift at a convenience store goes haywire when he is faced with a robbery, a shootout, and a homemade bomb in this pitch-black comedy.

465007.title: Crazy Mama
465007.description: An evicted mother (Ann Sothern) and daughter (Cloris Leachman) lead a cross-country 1950s crime spree.

466023.title: Running Scared
466023.description: Two policemen in wintry Chicago put off their tropical retirement plans when their nemesis, a ruthless drug dealer and murderer, evades custody.

466248.title: Dance Fu
466248.description: To avenge his uncle's murder, a wimpy dancer learns a unique style of martial arts that incorporates his jaw-dropping dance moves.

466619.title: Married to the Mob
466619.description: Living a normal life isn't easy for a mobster's widow when she attracts the attention of an enamored FBI agent and a married Mafioso.

466930.title: The Great Texas Dynamite Chase
466930.description: After busting out of the big house, a sexy jailbird picks up a feisty hitchhiker for a bank robbing binge that will soon become legendary.

466932.title: The Fiction Makers
466932.description: Gentleman thief Simon Templar gets mistaken for a mystery novelist by a gang of crooks, who force him to plan an extravagant heist.

467014.title: Toy Gun
467014.description: The black-comic tale of a meek man, who robs a bank to prove his grit to his wife, finds him on terra nova with a bundle of cash and a new ex-con pal.

468469.title: Frauds
468469.description: A conniving insurance investigator plays a twisted game of cat and mouse with a yuppie couple that makes an out-of-the ordinary insurance claim.

475182.title: Bitter Melon
475182.description: A Filipino-American family in San Francisco abused by an older brother get caught up in the youngest brother’s plan to murder him at Christmas.

475482.title: Women Who Kill
475482.description: Locally famous true-crime podcasters, who are also ex-girlfriends, suspect a new love interest is a serial killer in this deadpan comedy.

475898.title: Heathers
475898.description: When a snobbish high school clique threatens to ruin her reputation, a teenage girl teams up with a sociopath and plots to kill the cool kids.

476670.title: Nobel Son
476670.description: The night before an arrogant chemist receives the Nobel Prize, his son is kidnapped, but he refuses to pay the ransom, and a venomous tale unfolds.

476908.title: Killer Looks
476908.description: An alcoholic private detective and a sarcastic woman who loves kung-fu films team up to solve the murders of a fashion photographer and his models.

486598.title: Mad Dog Time
486598.description: After a mob boss is released from the mental hospital, his friends, family, and cronies, scramble to readjust the dynamics of their business.

489926.title: Avenging Angelo
489926.description: A dead mobster's daughter tries to reject her father's criminal past, but danger comes for her anyway, forcing a loyal bodyguard to intervene.

494075.title: Joyland
494075.description: A young convict’s decision to celebrate his last weekend on house arrest with a kickback party runs the risk of having his impending freedom revoked.

494830.title: Close But No Cigar
494830.description: A man and his dimwit companion help with the sale of an old VW van and are thrust into the clutches of criminals, debt collectors, and a psychopath.

495394.title: Bank Robber
495394.description: When a hopeless romantic tries to impress his thrill-seeking lover by robbing a bank, the heist goes wrong, sending him into hiding and another life.

495751.title: Freeway 2: Confessions of a Trickbaby
495751.description: A teen prostitute teams up with a serial killer to break out of prison and escape to Mexico. It’s an adventurous road movie like you've never seen.

495958.title: Cemetery High
495958.description: Creepy guys are hunted down by a group of revenge-driven, well-armed high school girls who are tired of being treated like objects.

499720.title: Live Wires
499720.description: Bowery Boys crime caper about the hijinks that ensue when one of the slackers gets a job with the D.A. to serve warrants to difficult locals in town.

499733.title: Hello Gangster
499733.description: Friendship, revenge and redemption collide when a man whose dog loves him unconditionally is taken from him, sending him on a quest to find her.

499792.title: Girltrash: All Night Long
499792.description: Over the course of one epic night in LA, two musicians headed for a battle of the bands instead find car trouble, girl trouble and a vengeful ex-con.

500477.title: Vacation!
500477.description: Four college girlfriends reunite for a vacation on the beach to drink and party, but a random drug buy causes a much different and tragic trip.

504272.title: Barking Dogs Never Bite
504272.description: When a graduate student with a pregnant wife tries to get rid of an incessantly barking dog in his apartment complex, things come back to bite him.

504668.title: Some Guy Who Kills People
504668.description: Having his life destroyed by a high school gang that bound, gagged and beat him, a man exacts the ultimate revenge on each of his tormentors.

505248.title: Imperfections
505248.description: A struggling actress works with a diamond importer, but when she becomes involved in a heist, everything quickly spirals into chaos.

505253.title: Kid Cannabis
505253.description: For a high school dropout and his slacker friend, trafficking marijuana across the Canadian border seems like the perfect scheme...until it’s not.

505297.title: Stark Raving Mad
505297.description: A thief plans to rob the boss who murdered his brother, but first he has to assemble the ultimate heist team to execute his vision flawlessly.

505417.title: Going to Brazil
505417.description: After a wild party in Rio, where a guest is killed, four girlfriends flee from the beaches to posh embassies to the rainforest, on a mad adventure.

508003.title: Detective K: Secret of Virtuous Widow
508003.description: When the king enlists his top detective to investigate a series of murders, the undercover case uncovers a massive government conspiracy.

510902.title: Kid Cop
510902.description: Determined to emulate his police officer dad who died on duty, an 11-year-old boy gets in over his head trying to solve a big local robbery case.

511099.title: Lobster Cop
511099.description: When undercover cops set up a drug sting in a seafood restaurant, they risk blowing their cover when their lobster recipe becomes an accidental hit.

511110.title: A Cool Fish
511110.description: A former cop turned security guard is sent back into police work after his sister is kidnapped. Can he save her before it’s too late?

512313.title: Soft Money
512313.description: A rich banker hires thieves to steal a million dollars from his own bank, but when he double-crosses the crooks, they hatch an elaborate revenge plot.

512437.title: Funland
512437.description: When mobsters buy out an amusement park, its newly fired mascot clown teams up with a hand puppet and Humphrey Bogart wax figurine to seek revenge.

512716.title: The Fuzz
512716.description: As a violent crime wave rocks Puppet Town, a puppet cop and his hapless human partner track down a dangerous drug dealer called Rainbow Brown.

513049.title: Baked in Brooklyn
513049.description: A guy with no income, two roommates, and a long-suffering girlfriend comes up with a way-out-of-the-box solution: selling marijuana over the Internet.

514022.title: Assault of the Killer Bimbos
514022.description: When two go-go dancers are framed for murder by a sleazy gangster, they begin a wild ride, picking up a waitress on the way toward Mexico and freedom.

514414.title: Bearkittens
514414.description: Petra is an idealistic social worker and about to enter her favorite place, the forest, with a group of young girls who have to do community service for their misdeeds. Little does she know that this trip will end in disaster.

518720.title: The Act
518720.description: A caper full of wild intrigue includes a bribed US president, blackmail, prison escapes, and a complex heist, in a plot where nothing is as it seems.

519525.title: The Hot Potato
519525.description: In 1969 London, as the Beatles top the charts and the US and USSR vie for power, two East End lads try to find a buyer for a lump of stolen uranium.

522440.title: Vice Academy 5
522440.description: Sexy vice cops must stop a virtual reality prostitute’s crime spree when a police commissioner’s son somehow uploads her out of a naughty video game.

524398.title: Know Nothins
524398.description: Following a successful heist, five professionals celebrate in a summer home while they wait for the final piece of the plan to fall into place.

526257.title: Hot Guys With Guns
526257.description: The detective bug bites two ex-boyfriends who team up with a jaded private investigator to solve a robbery spree targeting a gay Hollywood sex club.

527775.title: Get Bossy
527775.description: A weed-loving female detective partners with a bitter ex-CIA officer to reveal the conspiracy set by a notorious corporate villain out to get her.

528713.title: The Mafia Kills Only in Summer
528713.description: The Cosa Nostra’s reign of crime in 1970s Sicily unfolds through the eyes of a young boy obsessed with both the Mafia and his schoolmate crush.

530104.title: No Hay Más Remedio
530104.description: Arrepentidos de su tiempo perdido, tres hombres mayores deciden robar una farmacia, pero las cosas no les salen tan bien como lo planearon.

530110.title: El Día de la bestia
530110.description: Un sacerdote católico, un ocultista italiano y un metalero tratan de cometer la mayor cantidad de pecados para prevenir que el diablo nazca de nuevo.

530138.title: The Reluctant Agent
530138.description: When an undercover agent breaks her leg during a mission, the FBI enlists her estranged twin sister, who works as a waitress, to finish the job.

535964.title: Kill Your Friends
535964.description: A ruthless music exec searches for the last hit music act of the London pop scene while killing off any rivals in his drunken, drugged-out haze.

536585.title: Lucky Losers: Leo Gorcey & the Bowery Boys
536585.description: Slip and Sach suspect an illegal casino in the death of their boss so they go undercover as croupiers and a rich gambler to catch their criminals.

540196.title: Cain and Abel
540196.description: This modern LA tale with a strong '70's vibe, tells of an outlaw cop team on the hunt for a dangerous gangster with a gold-plated wheelchair.

543202.title: Homewrecker
543202.description: As a prisoner on work release, Mike just wants to be the best locksmith he can be. Until he meets a woman on the verge of a mental breakdown.

543930.title: The Magician
543930.description: A charismatic, rough hitman in Melbourne, Australia hires his film student next-door neighbor to film a documentary about his darkly humorous life.

547008.title: Capulina y Chespirito: Operación Carambola
547008.description: Un falso agente de seguridad nombra a Capulina su ayudante, pero pronto se da cuenta de que solamente lo están usando como carnada.

547021.title: El Investigador Capulina
547021.description: Creyendo que se las sabe de todas todas, se mete de detective, pero sus amigos los justicieros tendrán que salvarle el pellejo cada vez.

550383.title: Butt Boy
550383.description: A detective suspects his AA sponsor may be involved in a missing persons investigation when people start disappearing up the man’s butt.

551731.title: Silent Night, Dead Night
551731.description: The seedy side of Christmas comes alive in this bastardized Dickens tale that pits Ebenezer Scrooge and his prostitution ring against the mafia.

556726.title: Baby Doll
556726.description: Los Angeles is not the playground of Hollywood dreams that three beautiful Russian girlfriends think they’ll find when they arrive seeking stardom.

557050.title: Drowning Mona
557050.description: A Sheriff investigating the murder of an upstate New York woman learns that her extremely hateful ways gave the whole town a motive to be rid of her.

561230.title: Kill the Habit
561230.description: When a woman accidentally kills her drug dealer, she and her pals try to dispose of the corpse, as addicts looking for a fix keep getting in the way.

565421.title: Viruta Y Capulina: Dos Meseros Majaderos
565421.description: En un centro nocturno de mucho caché, el disparatado par acaba envuelto en una investigación policiaca y en la mira de un peligroso asesino.

569474.title: Compadres
569474.description: Fast-paced comedy about a Mexican, no-nonsense police officer and an American teen computer hacker who team up for a crime boss’s downfall.

571558.title: Shooting Fish
571558.description: Dylan and Jez are two orphans who are over-qualified and under employed. Tired of the "rich get richer" syndrome, they decide to make a million pounds each in London. They use every scam possible to achieve this, until Georgie comes into their lives. She needs lots of money and Dylan and Jez are the ones to get it for her.

571583.title: Who Is Cletis Tout?
571583.description: After two inmates escape prison and one steals a murdered tabloid reporter’s identity to finish a diamond heist, he soon finds he’s a hitman’s target.

573797.title: Dead or Alive 2: Tôbôsha
573797.description: Two fearsome Yakuza assassin rivals decide to reunite as the childhood friends they are and start over in their homeland after a hit goes wrong.

575231.title: Bullet Ride
575231.description: In the red for five million dollars, a duo of film producers hatch a plan to make their latest feature a success by killing off its star actor.

578576.title: Pork Pie
578576.description: A trio of young misfits in pursuit of lost love race the length of the country in a stolen Mini Cooper S. Avoiding the law and with nothing to lose, they become folk heroes and most wanted criminals as they find themselves caught in the crosshairs of a media frenzy and an escalating police operation.

579499.title: Luck-Key
579499.description: Two strangers meet at a public bathhouse, not knowing what happens in their lives: Hyung-wook is a world-class killer with a 100% success rate. He always wears a high-end suit and expensive watches. When doing his usual job, a drop of blood taints his shirt sleeve, and he visits the bathhouse to erase the stain. Meanwhile, Jae-sung, an unemployed actor, visit the bathhouse to get the final 'cleansing' before killing himself. Their lives switch when Hyung-wook slides on a bar of soap and hit his head on the floor. Jae-sung steals Hyung-wook's locker key, in hopes of living a luxurious life just for a day. Hyung-wook eventually regains consciousness, but he remembers nothing. He just assumes he is Jae-sung, based on what remains to him. He starts to live the life of an unknown actor, but his instinct and training give him an unexpected chance for an acting career.

579552.title: Cul-De-Sac
579552.description: On a small island off the coast of England, two escaped convicts find their hide out in the dank castle of a recluse and his undersexed wife.

579564.title: N.Y.P.D. Mounted
579564.description: The unlikely partnership of a rodeo cowboy and a jaded cop lead to all sorts of hijinks in New York City’s horse-riding law enforcement unit.

581121.title: Down the Drain
581121.description: A slimy underworld lawyer plots the ultimate bank robbery with some former clients, which invites chaos into his and his girlfriend’s life.

581174.title: The Girl Gets Moe
581174.description: When a ruthless mobster falls in love, he tries to change his life. But when his partner makes a deadly mistake, his new love turns on him.

581303.title: Lowdown Dirty Criminals
581303.description: Two friends with no criminal background wind up in a hilarious jam after a mobster hires them and they proceed to utterly fail at all of their jobs.

589292.title: The Mask
589292.description: Jim Carrey’s superstar role as a kind and meek bank teller who gets super powers from a Nordic mask and becomes a totally s-s-s-smokin’ hero!

589582.title: Porches And Private Eyes Two
589582.description: After getting a taste of sleuthing success, the Southern belles use their newly found mystery solving skills to track down a supernatural killer.

590502.title: Rook.
590502.description: After a pair of siblings and a small group attempt a gold heist and miserably fail, they most contend with hillbilly brothers ready to fight back.

591183.title: The Black Ball
591183.description: A middle-aged shopkeeper goes way off the deep end to figure out why he got downvoted by a local members-only club he tried to join.

593656.title: Snowman's Land
593656.description: After a professional killer botches a job, he heads to a remote region with his sidekick, but they soon realize that their bad luck doesn’t end there.

593857.title: Scotland, PA
593857.description: The classic intrigue of Shakespeare’s “Macbeth” comes to the suburbs of Philly in the 1970s as a hamburger vendor is influenced by his scheming wife.

595171.title: The Bingo Robbers
595171.description: Vallis lives in his 76 Chrysler. Nancy is a single mom and desperate. The two cruise the shadowy streets of Newfoundland's biggest city bringing us their darkly comic observations, while plotting the best way to take down the 24 hour Bingo Extravaganza.

596148.title: Terminal Exposure
596148.description: Two beach combing-shutterbugs accidentally capture a murder on film. Now detectives, the boys set out to capture a murderess shot only from behind, with a rose tattoo on her behind. Fun in the sun turns dangerous when they end up shooting bullets instead of film.

596909.title: L.A. Superheroes: Illegal in Hollywood
596909.description: A gorgeous immigrant and her guy try to make it in Hollywood and stay true to their hearts, taking on weasley agents, mobsters, the FBI, and nut jobs.

597383.title: The Deadbeats
597383.description: A man who works as a pirate clown for birthday parties has a bad gig that gets worse when he’s heckled by a pack of deadbeats who cause him to snap.

599266.title: How to Win Enemies
599266.description: Lucas, a young lawyer meets the stunning, sexy Bárbara in a café. Lucas, thinks she is perfect, with a taste for good literature. Lucas takes her home on his first date. The next morning Lucas wakes up to find Bárbara gone together with his cash hoard. Determined to recover his money he tracks her down, but is shocked to find the identity of the person behind the heist.

601997.title: Night Shift
601997.description: When their mother dies, two destitute brothers rob a gas station to save their family home, but when things go wrong, they start taking hostages.

602010.title: The Last Diamond
602010.description: After being released from prison, a man plots out how he will steal a famous diamond, but his teammate’s motives aren’t what they seem.

602977.title: Bank Brothers
602977.description: A trio of plumbers from the hood unwittingly foil a high-level mob insurance scam when they decide to enter the dangerous world of jewel theft.

604280.title: Shut Up and Shoot!
604280.description: A movie producer hatches a scheme to have an actor (Silvio Pollio) kill his fellow filmmakers (James Russo, John Savage, Gary Busey, Tom Sizemore, Daniel Baldwin).

604310.title: Robin-B-Hood
604310.description: Thongs and Octopus grow attached to the baby they kidnapped for their landlord, which leads to complications in handing the him over.

604717.title: Clover
604717.description: Two brothers "Irish Twins"- down on their luck, and in debt to a dangerous crime boss, must go on the run to save themselves, and a seemingly innocent teenage girl, after a job goes wrong, and she kills the crime boss’s only son.

605690.title: One-Line
605690.description: A young con artist thinks he’s hit the big time when he’s recruited to join a bank loan scam run by a group of double-dealing professional thieves.

605700.title: The Grand Heist
605700.description: When corrupt officials corner the ice market, a gang of professionals from various fields goes on a mission to rob ice blocks from their storage unit.

606362.title: Have a Nice Day (Subbed)
606362.description: A gritty animated crime drama about a man who steals a million in cash from his boss and soon has equally greedy characters wanting it for themselves.

610165.title: Keep an Eye Out
610165.description: Set in a 1970’s police station, this is the story of a man who discovers a dead body, becomes the prime suspect, and experiences an unusual night.

610237.title: The Adventures of Rat Pfink and Boo Boo
610237.description: A rock singer and a gardener transform into caped crusaders to stop three criminals who intend to kidnap an unsuspecting young woman.

614782.title: Mama Weed
614782.description: A translator with the Paris police (Isabelle Huppert) finds herself in possession of a huge store ofhash, the insider knowledge required to move it and an unexpected flair for the danger that ensues.

617337.title: Billion
617337.description: When a high-powered banker loses all of his wealth, he’ll need to call on his estranged children to help him carry out a heist of his own bank.

617518.title: Midnight Runners
617518.description: A pair of goofy students at a police academy witness a kidnapping and decide to solve the crime themselves, despite their lack of experience.

618589.title: Goodbye Paradise
618589.description: In 1980s Queensland, a disgraced ex-cop  writes an expose on police corruption, unveils a religious cult, and witnesses the start of  a military coup.

620085.title: Enter the Fat Dragon
620085.description: Action icon Donnie Yen stars as a super cop who becomes depressed and obese after a break-up and just before he gets a murder case to save his job.

628297.title: Bhagam Bhag
628297.description: Two immature actors end up involved in a criminal mix-up after their behavior causes their leading lady to quit while they are ordered to replace her.

629134.title: Dymez
629134.description: Three desperate young women plan heists using an app on their smartphones, unaware of just how dangerous the situation is about to get.

631449.title: Masti
631449.description: Three best friends who are over their respective marriages decide it’s time to have affairs, except they end up as framed murder suspects instead.

631475.title: Aflatoon
631475.description: A grifter with a plan to become an instant millionaire by marrying an heiress gets his plans foiled by a series of crimes committed by his lookalike.

636847.title: Big News
636847.description: On the verge of losing both his wife and his job, a talented but boozing reporter on a criminal conspiracy invetsigation gets framed for murder.

636855.title: Billy the Kid in Texas
636855.description: After robbing the outlaw gang that just ripped off a payroll, new arrival Billy the Kid is elected sheriff to bring order to a lawless Texas town.

637069.title: 9 Stacks
637069.description: A young man finds himself caught up in a matter of business fraud and has to choose whether to call it out or try to escape the consequences.

639880.title: Born to Win
639880.description: A smart-mouthed former hairdresser, turned  junkie and loser, commits a variety of petty crimes and spends his days looking for just "one more fix.”

642389.title: Band of Robbers
642389.description: Mark Twain’s reimagined characters, Tom Sawyer and Huck Finn, now grown men, continue to search for the treasure that has eluded them since childhood.

645491.title: Sweet and Lowdown
645491.description: Sean Penn stars as a gifted but mercurial jazz guitarist in the 1930s whose struggles with envy and mobsters are changed by his love for a mute woman.

650509.title: Say My Name
650509.description: After a one-night stand is interrupted by a botched robbery, the new couple must navigate the underbelly of a Welsh isle to get their property back.

650521.title: The Case of the Lucky Legs
650521.description: A con man who stages phony “lucky legs” beauty contests and leaves town with the money is found with a surgical knife in his heart by Perry Mason.

655403.title: SGT. Kabukiman N.Y.P.D.
655403.description: An ancient prophecy transforms a bumbling NYPD detective into the world's oddest superhero to take on evil corporations and drug-dealing ministers.

660765.title: Hostage for a Day
660765.description: A middle-aged man, tired of his nagging wife and dreary job, tries to escape his humdrum existence and start life anew, by faking his own kidnapping.

667942.title: Honest
667942.description: In late-1960’s swinging London, the All Saints girls play three streetwise sisters who head 'up West' to cheat, steal and generally cause trouble.

672059.title: Schemers
672059.description: A young man looks to turn a fast buck running discos to impress a nurse trainee he is in love with and avoid getting an office job.

672671.title: Good Girls Don't
672671.description: A bold and daring stripper and mousey secretary go on the lam in a red convertible after being framed for a murder they didn't commit.

673108.title: Dead Body
673108.description: Criminal high jinks ensue in this madcap comedy about two lifelong friends, Jason and Craig, who must come together to dispose of a dead body.

673112.title: PPP Loan Gone
673112.description: Jacob Stone gets caught up in a scheme, influenced by his best friend Shaun Murra, to use falsified information to get approved for a PPP loan.

675213.title: Buffet Froid
675213.description: Three men—an unemployed young man, a police chief-inspector, and a killer—are thrown into a series of events in a surrealist world.

675356.title: Legacy
675356.description: Three of the most popular girls of a sorority, Lana, Mai, and Zoey, become prime suspects when a geeky rushee is found dead on campus.

676862.title: 68 Kill
676862.description: A robbery gone wrong sends a hapless guy and his psychotic girlfriend on a seriously wild ride in this deranged, off-the-rails blast of insanity.

677077.title: Arizona
677077.description: In this darkly comedic story, Cassie, a real estate agent and single mom, struggles to keep it all together during the housing crisis of 2009.

680568.title: Super
680568.description: A super-entertaining action fantasy about a down-on-his-luck fry cook who becomes a homegrown masked avenger and puts an end to crimes.

682042.title: Once Upon a Time in Venice
682042.description: Venice Beach P.I. Steve Ford is a detective who's good with the ladies, bad with the punches, and absolutely wild about his dog, Buddy.

684128.title: Sightseers
684128.description: A hilarious comedy about a young couple who embark on a romantic road trip that unintentionally turns into a slew of entertaining errors.

685148.title: Trapped by Television

687649.title: Cop Secret
687649.description: Iceland's toughest cop will stop at nothing to solve a string of violent bank robberies. But pressures mount when he's forced to take a new partner.

688033.title: The Pizzagate Massacre

689436.title: The Alarmist

693890.title: Tomorrow's Today

694683.title: Double Nickels

695065.title: Killer Whales

697775.title: Loose Change
697775.description: A down-on-his-luck street magician and his con artist ex-wife reunite to swindle an accounting firm in this dark comedy.

699312.title: The Accidental Detective
699312.description: A cold-case enthusiast blogger and a washed-up veteran detective join forces to rescue their innocent friend from a murder charge.

706262.title: Sometimes Aunt Martha Does Dreadful Things

707152.title: Dancer and the Dame
707152.description: When a detective teams up with a demanding police dog with psychological issues of her own, the two get a second chance to set the record straight.

707555.title: Max Bishop

708805.title: Susie Q

709513.title: Beach Volleyball Detectives (Pt. 1)

709667.title: Full-Dress

714836.title: Murder by the Book

715988.title: Big Shots
715988.description: The search for a stolen wristwatch unites a coddled, suburban white boy grieving his father’s death and a streetwise Black boy as partners in crime.

716292.title: Burglar

0300005273.title: Bounty Hunters

0300006340.title: Vexed

0300007975.title: America's Dumbest Criminals

0300008794.title: Filth City

03962.title: Tropical Heat

0300007243.title: The Spot 313

0189.title: Outrageous Fortune

0300005766.title: Tenspeed and Brownshoe
